{"tid":449566,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"虛報遭強姦　美容師判100小時社服令","createTime":"2017-10-27T09:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T13:48:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1290f83e6f949d5d11b838768c70ef9d486096e0","tid":449566,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T09:54:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171027/20195876\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171027%2F20195876&d=MX0V4rhuZCBpOgK%2F7GxHbIM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=c5541154\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171027%2F20195876&h=87fbafa7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171027/20195876</a><br />\n<br />\n虛報遭強姦　美容師判100小時社服令<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】30歲美容師於街頭遇上陌生男子主動兜搭，深信兩人可成為情侶，交往不久便同意與對方到酒店開房，不料男子其後便失去蹤影。美容師從網絡流傳的「賤男名單」找到男子電話，認為遇上情場騙子，遂報假案訛稱遭強姦，但酒店閉路電視拍到兩人入房前後表現親熱，揭發她報假案。美容師早前認罪，昨判罰100小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171027/large/a1202a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171027%2Flarge%2Fa1202a.gif&h=d0e39ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告鍾家怡昨被判社會服務令後離開。謝榮耀攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官指情節獨特<br />\n<br />\n辯方指被告鍾家怡的社會服務令報告正面，裁判官指被告沒案底，本案情節獨特，適合判服務令。案情指被告於8月31日報案，稱姓周的男友人3天前在酒店強姦她。周被捕後指獲同意下才性交，警員翻查閉路電視發現二人進出酒店時有拖手及接吻，再發現二人之前已有性接觸。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC2831/17<br />\n■記者歐陽聯發"},{"pid":"cdae705793cc0b457eb785660932870d6925c5a9","tid":449566,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T09:56:17.000Z","msg":"個賤男真係無法無天 咁都挫佢唔入 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5419259a181b274b07904b2d8f3124c87b469823","tid":449566,"uid":146769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T09:56:26.000Z","msg":"細個玩電腦大富翁去到法院告人失敗既話要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 坐監"},{"pid":"74401648892682c23e209d3c0c240a39795b7148","tid":449566,"uid":26752,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T09:56:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>老屈低成本<br />\n<br />\n女權萬歲</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faab3ccdb3bed9c67f3c2095c927d4de0387ef12","tid":449566,"uid":7534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T09:57:48.000Z","msg":"勞<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>"},{"pid":"34e6614b1eb1e2bdeef5eec618cf41a88c755f38","tid":449566,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T09:57:49.000Z","msg":"臭雞一名"},{"pid":"2cea7b7a691391f86a9bad4614a58bcd8cd66e84","tid":449566,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:11:12.000Z","msg":"應該判比人姦番100小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fa5b101cdfcac0af3d3fbf01d4e0122ca0b190a","tid":449566,"uid":1611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:12:53.000Z","msg":"人格謀殺罰得個100個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5cfae4f81b1aee9e5181c06dd0140afa8730510","tid":449566,"uid":40932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:39:38.000Z","msg":"100個鐘服務令 vs 坐幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屈人強奸應該要坐牢啦"},{"pid":"84050546ea5c0b908c5852e3b2441098ce8577b9","tid":449566,"uid":36995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T13:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>100個鐘服務令 vs 坐幾年<im